{
  "stem": "26983.10",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 22.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were-- we saw around us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One camp after the other was emptied.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went still with the Rollwagen, I remember, to the abandoned [NON-ENGLISH], which was next to us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was nobody there anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And why do I remember it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we went in the abandoned kitchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, only the Mannerlager were still few-- I mean, some maybe, a couple of thousand prisoners.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we saw salt in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Salt.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we took it in the camp, and we made business with--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something very important.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not in such-- but suddenly, we saw a lot of salt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we brought it, and we sold it to other prisoners.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for that we got, let's say, four cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And four cigarettes was equivalent of a ration or a half of bread, or whatever we got.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember the cigarettes, by the way, a little before, were [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yosma ?] and Corfu because the Greek people who, at that time in summer '44, the Germans, I think, occupied Corfu or one of these islands, and these prisoners brought with them [?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yosma ?] and Corfu.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember, even, a group of Greek Jews who came to our camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was difficult to speak with them because they spoke only Greek.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we could somehow, in between us, understand each other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "By the way, once, to Theresienstadt, came a group of children from Bialystok--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--which were isolated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had to live in Theresienstadt completely isolated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they came from Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people who had some contact with them told us they were terribly afraid to take a shower.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were starting to scream, 'Gas!",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Gas!' And we only know that there were some volunteers who worked with them from Theresienstadt--",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
